Dear all,
We are excited to announce our upcoming course on Interactive Maps with R, and we wanted to reach out to inform you that we have the last seats available!
Course Details:
Title: Interactive Maps with R
Dates: 22-23 June 2023
Format: Online (to foster international participation)
